casebody.data:
Charles Alonzo TUNSTALL
v.
Frank W. BALLANCE, etal. No. 323A92-10. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Sept. 24, 2015. Charles Alonzo Tunstall, for Tunstall, Charles Alonzo. Derrick Mertz, Assistant Attorney General, for State of N.C.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Petitioner on the 14th of August 2015 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 24th of September 2015."
